/*
Face 2AFC / YN Training Script
================================
Training Stages:
  0 : Fixation reward (immediate)
  1 : Fixation hold reward
  2 : Stimulus + mask toleration (auto reward, no response)
  3 : Full 2AFC — full contrast, response required
        correction_enabled toggleable
  4 : Fade-to-YN — one side alpha 1→0 via 3-down-1-up staircase
        blank side randomized (either face or scrambled, either left or right)
        correction_enabled toggleable
  5 : Full YN — blank side fully gone (alpha=0), response required
        correction_enabled toggleable
  6 : Block switching — 2AFC + YN interleaved at full contrast
        correction_enabled toggleable
  7 : Calibration — 3-down-1-up staircase on stimulus contrast
        both 2AFC and YN interleaved
        correction_enabled toggleable
*/

